item.content:encoded:
Look at this happy little mushroom looking at us in these mushroom coloring pages! Think about where he might be going as you color in his bright red cap and white polka dot spots. Maybe he’s off to meet up with his fun mushroom friends for a play date! You can even draw in some vibrant green grass and colorful wildflowers at his feet to complete the lively forest scene.
On PC Click the left mouse button or tap the screen to draw.On mobile Use your finger to touch the screen.
